'''胡瓜魚目'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|Osmeriformes}}）是[[輻鰭魚綱|輻鰭魚綱]]的一個[[目_(生物)|目]]。

==分类==
本目属于[[正真骨鱼群|正真骨鱼群]]的[[巨口鱼亚群|巨口鱼亚群]]，[[巨口鱼目|巨口鱼目]]是本目的[[姐妹群|姐妹群]]{{r|deepfin}}。

本目下分4[[科_(生物)|科]]<ref>Nelson, J.S. 1994. [[世界鱼类|Fishes of the World]]. John Wiley and Sons, Inc. New York. 3rd edition. ISBN 0-471-54713-1</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fishbase.org/Summary/OrdersSummary.php?Order=Osmeriformes |title=FishBase: Order Summary for Osmeriformes |access-date=2012-02-11 |archive-date=2020-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204170231/https://www.fishbase.org/summary/OrdersSummary.php?Order=Osmeriformes |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{r|deepfin}}：
*[[後鰭魚亞目|後鰭魚亞目]] Retropinnoidei
**[[後鰭魚科|後鰭魚科]] Retropinnidae
*[[胡瓜魚亞目|胡瓜魚亞目]] Osmeroidei
**[[胡瓜魚科|胡瓜魚科]] Osmeridae
**[[香魚科|香魚科]] Plecoglossidae
**[[銀魚科|銀魚科]] Salangidae

过去有一些曾被归类在这里的科已被分类到新的、独立的目[[水珍魚目|水珍魚目]]（{{lang-en|Argentiniformes}}）<ref>{{aut|Diogo, Rui}} (2008): On the cephalic and pectoral girdle muscles of the deep sea fish ''Alepocephalus rostratus'', with comments on the functional morphology and phylogenetic relationships of the Alepocephaloidei (Teleostei). ''[[Animal_Biology_(journal)|Anim. Biol.]]'' '''58'''(1): 23-29. {{doi|10.1163/157075608X303636}}</ref>。

